data.description: Experience pure perfection in this meticulously maintained two-story haven. The full brick exterior exudes elegance and durability. Inside, formal charm blends seamlessly with cozy relaxation. The versatile 1st-floor office/5th bedroom adds flexibility. The masterpiece kitchen boasts stainless appliances, an island, and pantry. Hardwood floors add a touch of luxury. Upstairs, the owner's suite is a retreat with cathedral ceilings and a luxurious bath featuring a dual sink vanity, soaking tub, and step-in shower. The walkout basement with large windows and plumbing rough-ins presents endless possibilities. Community perks include a clubhouse and basketball court. With easy access to I-275, shopping, and dining, this isn't just a home - it's a lifestyle upgrade.
